   att.datable.custom (attribute class)

      @when-custom


      @notBefore-custom


      @notAfter-custom


      @from-custom


      @to-custom


      @datingPoint


      @datingMethod

 provides attributes for normalization of elements that contain datable events to a custom dating system (i.e. other than the Gregorian used by W3 and ISO). [13.3.7. Dates and Times]

